data.description: Welcome home to this low maintenance 4 sided brick ranch near fabulous downtown Lawrenceville. The Chefs Kitchen features an open view to the living room with wood burning fireplace insert. Spacious Dining room provides plenty of room to gather or unwind in the sizable sitting room. The cozy Owners Suite is accompanied by an en-suite with tile shower. Two additional secondary bedrooms share a bath. Relax on the rocking chair front porch or retire to the back deck overlooking the private backyard with 16'x20' wired storage building. Camelot is a quiet neighborhood close to downtown Lawrenceville with all of its unique festivals, shops, restaurants, concerts and nightlife! No HOA!! All appliances stay!! New Roof and Gutters. Convenient to I-85, Hwy 316, Athens and Atlanta. 2021-07-13
